high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Slice the lettuce in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn right, move to the end of the counter, near the pan and plant.
Put the lettuce slice in the pan.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the pan in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with lettuce in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left at the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Slice the lettuce in the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the sink
Turn around, go to the edge of the counter
Put the lettuce in the pan on the counter
Pick up the pan on the counter
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left, go forward, turn right and go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce, put a slice into the pan, put the pan in the fridge

high_descs: Turn right and face the sink on your right.
Take the silver knife from the sink in front of you.
Slice the lettuce in the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Take a lettuce slice from the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter with the pan in front of you.
Place the lettuce slice on the pan on the counter in front of you.
Take the pan from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the fridge on your right.
Place the pan with the lettuce in the fridge and close it.
